  <RulesElement name="Goblin - Hexer" type="Background" internal-id="ID_MSR_BACKGROUND_203" source="ObMeiste" revision-date="10/5/2010 1:34:59 PM">
    <specific name="type"> Controller </specific>
    <specific name="Common Knowledge"> The Hexers have the mantle of spellcasters and fortune tellers of sorts in the tribe. They practice the dark art of curses, something well sought after by goblins to bring upon their foes and to have avoid having above their own head. As there is no need to make a short dangerous life even more so. For this reason the Hexers are treated well, but with suspicion (Though rarely obviously so)
When called to battle for the sake of the tribe, they create areas that conceals their allies within and which disrupt their foes attacks. </specific>
    <specific name="Benefit"> Features
-Trickster: You gain the thievery skill as a class skill. If your selected class already has it listed you gain +2 bonus to that skill
-Dabbler: You gain the ritual or alchemist caster feat.
-Vexing Cloud: You gain the vexing cloud Encounter power. </specific>
